July 24, 2017 6:48 AM ET
Electric Utilities

Company Overview of Huntley Power LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Huntley Power LLC is a 720 MW coal fired power plant based in Tonawanda, New York. Huntley Power LLC operates as a subsidiary of NRG Energy, Inc.


1221 Nicollet MallSuite 700Minneapolis, MN 55403-2445United States



Phone: 612-373-5300








